TY  - JOUR
T1  - Majority Decisions and Transitivity: Some Special Cases
AU  - Merchant, Deepak K.
AU  - Rao, M. R.
Y1  - 1976/10/01
PY  - 1976
DA  - 1976/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.23.2.125
